name: Code Geass: Lost Stories
description: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion Lost Stories (コードギアス 反逆のルルーシュ ロストストーリーズ Kōdo Giasu: Hangyaku no Rurūshu Rosutosutōrīzu) is a game developed by f4samurai and DMM Games. It is a tower defense game released for smartphones and PCs, which launched in May of 2022.

name: Fallout 76: S.P.E.C.I.A.L. Edition
description: The edition, in addition to Fallout 76 game, consists of a set of three pin badges from the Fallout S.P.E.C.I.A.L attribute range, the ruleset that powers all Fallout games and an acronym standing for the primary statistics in the system: Strength, Perception, Endurance, Charisma, Intelligence, Agility and Luck. This edition features the Strength, Charisma & Luck attributes.

name: Atlas: Groundbreaking Adventures
description: Atlas is an action-rpg with rogue-like elements where you use your ability to control the ground to fight the enemies and move through procedurally generated worlds.

name: Mobile Ball
description:
Mobile Ball is a character-based sports game that was planned for release in Japan on Nintendo 3DS, iOS and Android. 
The game was based on soccer with up to 3v3 multiplayer that supported crossplay. 
The characters had unique abilities and power-ups or items would be in the arena as well. 
 
Originally planned for release in Q4 2018, the game was delayed to early 2019 to improve its quality. In April it was further delayed to mid 2019. 
The game's cancellation was announced on June 20th 2019 after not achieving the quality the developer was aiming for.

name: Risk One's Neck
description: Feel the excitement again! Risk One's Neck is an arcade-style beat'em up game in a brand new, thrilling, and powerful way.

name: Dabado
description: Dabado is a Puzzle RPG game with unique hand-made art created by Viktor Mazhlekov, artist, game designer and animator, author of the animation - PORTALS. Game main goal is to inspire and fill people with positive mood.

name: ProBoon
description: This game is meant to bring back the old-school shooting action from the 90s. Made with sprites and low res textures, it offers a complete single player campaign and multiplayer with different modes, including co-op and deathmatch.

name: Fitzzle Cute Kittens
description: Hello puzzle solver! Fitzzle Cute Kittens is a unique expansion of the classic jigsaw puzzle style games. Instead of frustratingly trying to match oddly shaped pieces Fitzzle Cute Kittens uses squares but maintains the fun puzzle completion goals you would experience with a jigsaw puzzle.

Players in the game are alone in the Forest, and they can use axes, cut down trees and build freely to explore the surrounding things. In order to survive, players need to find at least 20 canned fish stocks to use, after the search can be cleared. 
WASD character control 
E pick up items and so on 
ESC brings up the menu to see how many cans are collected

In the game, the player must ride on his horse to use the weapon, destroy the enemy and find their own horse can win, must guarantee themselves and mount the amount of blood, the player can use the sword, pistol, bow and arrow on the horse to hurt the enemy, alive find another horse can win.

name: Nighthawks
description:
"Nighthawks is the brand new urban fantasy RPG from Wadjet Eye Games (The Blackwell Legacy, Unavowed, Technobabylon) and writer/designer Richard Cobbett (Sunless Sea/Sunless Skies, The Long Journey Home)."

"Nighthawks is a mix of story-driven RPG and undead life-simulation, where every decision you make is another move in your chess game against the world. Invest your time into learning new skills or honing your fighting style as you uncover the city's mysteries and venture deep into its darkest secrets. Gather fellow outcasts to your side, binding them with favours and choosing when to cash in. Manage your eternal thirst, legitimately, or balancing the risks of being caught stalking unwary victims and working the black markets."

Miniconomy has a great community with active and friendly players.

In the virtual economy, where everyone is on a mission and everyone plays a role, it's up to you to choose how you live your virtual life: Will you be going for riches, power, new friends, or would you rather be a politician?

The King has put the Kingdom's defense in the hands of the Order of the Green Harlequins, who have faithfully served the Kingdom for centuries.

More Grillin’ is the perfect summertime fun app for your iPhone, iPod Touch, or iPad. Fire up the virtual grill, throw on some burgers, hot dogs, veggie burgers or even steaks. Hear the sizzle and watch the flames dance, while you flip your food to cook it, then dress it up with dozens of sauces, toppings, and side dishes. All with sharpest graphics we’ve ever had (full resolution on iPhone/iPod Touch, iPad, and even iPhone 4 Retina Display!), and of course the attention to detail Maverick is known for.

After you’ve made your burger, bratwurst, or chicken, and given it the perfect presentation with custom plates & tablecloths, share a picture with your friends via email, Facebook, or save it to your photo album. And of course you can eat it! Take virtual bites and have your own picnic.

Swap colored beads on a spider's web to create matching chains and release letters to spell magical words. Each match you make will charge your mighty hammer with a bit of rainbow dust. When your hammer is ready, it can smash any bead, allowing you to spell the words you need more quickly! Between levels, you can use your magic to release cursed objects and restore the town! Rainbow Web 3 can provide hours of relaxing match-three challenges and captivating casual fun!

It all seems peaceful, but again the journey will be nothing like you expected it to be.
